1
00:00:08,260 --> 00:00:11,220
♪Dark clouds shroud the long trail
where the sun descends♪

2
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:13,980
♪Must we only meet by chance
and never again?♪

3
00:00:14,020 --> 00:00:16,900
♪To be parted forever in an instant♪

4
00:00:16,940 --> 00:00:19,660
♪Time flies never to be recalled♪

5
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:22,700
♪When your smile is embedded
in the starry night♪

6
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:25,740
♪We are puppets of twisted fates♪

7
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:28,620
♪Constantly intertwining♪

8
00:00:28,660 --> 00:00:31,660
♪Dissolving in the crowd♪

9
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:34,940
♪Perhaps out of reach and out of sight♪

10
00:00:34,940 --> 00:00:37,260
♪Constantly flashing through my dreams♪

11
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:45,100
♪The sudden icy wind blurs my vision♪

12
00:00:46,980 --> 00:00:50,660
♪The rain drew that day to an end♪

13
00:00:50,700 --> 00:00:54,380
♪How I wish your beauty♪

14
00:00:54,380 --> 00:00:59,460
♪I want to love you,
love you, love you, love you♪

15
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:10,820
[My Divine Emissary]

16
00:01:10,940 --> 00:01:13,780
[Episode 19]

17
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,440
What are you doing?

18
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,040
Originally,

19
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,760
I wanted to take photos
of the canal as a souvenir.

20
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:48,120
How is the canal nicer
to look at than me?

21
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,880
Of course, you're nicer to look at.

22
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:03,740
[Health]
What is this?

23
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:05,340
It's an amulet.

24
00:02:05,580 --> 00:02:07,140
It came from your bag.

25
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:11,340
This...

26
00:02:11,940 --> 00:02:13,700
It looks like someone cut it open,

27
00:02:13,820 --> 00:02:15,220
put the amulet inside,

28
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:16,180
and then sew it up.

29
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:18,660
But I bought the bag

30
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:20,020
just before I came to Qi Kingdom...

31
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:26,220
Mom, what are you doing?

32
00:02:26,220 --> 00:02:27,900
Didn't I tell you not to touch my bag?

33
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:29,180
As if I care about it.

34
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:31,940
You never work hard at your studies,

35
00:02:32,140 --> 00:02:33,620
but you're diligent at changing bags.

36
00:02:33,940 --> 00:02:35,420
Keep a few books in there.

37
00:02:38,140 --> 00:02:39,900
It was likely my mother.

38
00:02:40,980 --> 00:02:43,660
Is your relationship
with your mother bad?

39
00:02:43,860 --> 00:02:45,180
In her eyes,

40
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:46,540
a person is only good

41
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:47,700
if they have good grades.

42
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:48,900
I'm bad at my studies,

43
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:50,580
so she doesn't like everything about me.

44
00:02:50,580 --> 00:02:51,780
She always wants
to have control over me.

45
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:53,740
After school,
I have to go straight home.

46
00:02:53,740 --> 00:02:55,180
On the weekends, I have to sleep
and wake up early.

47
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:56,820
Food is always bland and healthy.

48
00:02:56,820 --> 00:02:58,260
Before I'm in university,
no dating is allowed.

49
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:01,820
How I envy you.

50
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:04,620
Envy?

51
00:03:06,180 --> 00:03:08,700
I was raised by my nursemaid.

52
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:11,460
It's hard for me to even see my mother.

53
00:03:11,740 --> 00:03:13,060
She is not at all interested

54
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:14,700
in my emotions and life.

55
00:03:15,740 --> 00:03:16,780
My existence

56
00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:18,140
is just another pawn

57
00:03:18,140 --> 00:03:19,620
for the Cui family
to solidify their power.

58
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,180
You should know

59
00:03:21,500 --> 00:03:22,660
in the palace,

60
00:03:22,820 --> 00:03:25,460
power is more important than family.

61
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:27,860
Qi Yan.

62
00:03:31,220 --> 00:03:32,780
That's why I envy you.

63
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:37,020
Your mother wants you
to go straight home after school.

64
00:03:37,580 --> 00:03:38,940
That's because she's worried
you would be in danger.

65
00:03:39,820 --> 00:03:40,980
Control over your diet

66
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,500
is for the sake of your health.

67
00:03:44,380 --> 00:03:45,300
Sometimes,

68
00:03:45,660 --> 00:03:47,740
parents like that are way too strict.

69
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:51,140
But in the end, it's because of love.

70
00:03:53,380 --> 00:03:56,020
I hear in this amulet,

71
00:03:56,620 --> 00:03:58,780
there would be a note hidden inside

72
00:03:59,180 --> 00:04:01,660
containing a wish or a prayer.

73
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:03,060
Do you want to open it to see?

74
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:06,900
Okay.

75
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,000
What?

76
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:23,420
I offer up my happiness and luck

77
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:25,980
in exchange for the health and safety
of my daughter, Li Mengmeng.

78
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:31,420
Not riches or power.

79
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:33,140
Not a bright future.

80
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:35,260
Just for your safety.

81
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:38,940
She must love you a lot.

82
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:41,880
What is it?

83
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:43,480
Don't cry.

84
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,320
Isn't this good?

85
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,440
Your mother loves you.

86
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:50,760
However,

87
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,680
she might not use the right way.

88
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:57,560
But I can't go back now.

89
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,200
Qi Yan,

90
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,720
I really miss her.

91
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,080
Did you know?

92
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:05,200
Before I left home,

93
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,840
I even fought with her.

94
00:05:15,180 --> 00:05:16,660
[Map of Qi Kingdom, Zhongzhou]

95
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:24,520
I can't believe a place like this exists

96
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,400
in the Imperial Study Room.

97
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:31,200
We have to act soon.

98
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:35,360
If we wait until he is fully grown,

99
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:39,000
we will not stand a chance.

100
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,360
Chancellor Cui, what is your plan?

101
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,760
His Majesty went
to hide from the heat, right?

102
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,480
We'll make it
so that he can't come back at all.

103
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,640
Send out the orders.

104
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:54,080
Ensure a strict guard
at every checkpoint from Yang City.

105
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:56,600
Immediately report
all suspicious persons.

106
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:57,880
Yes.

107
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,400
Hurry.

108
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,680
As per Chancellor Cui's command,

109
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,840
from today onward,

110
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,320
we will be assisting you
in guarding the gates.

111
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,960
Anyone coming into the city

112
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,400
must have
their identification documents.

113
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,920
Otherwise, they will be arrested.

114
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,240
Yes.

115
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:21,020
[Hua'an Gate]

116
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:29,740
[Sai Residence]

117
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,240
Your Highness is very skilled.

118
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,440
Second Prince.

119
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,280
What are you doing?

120
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,160
It's a cape.

121
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,600
Huai'an is always riding on horseback.

122
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,360
It's cold in the night.

123
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,680
I have some spare time,

124
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,800
so I made him a cape.

125
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:58,840
Prince Heqin is so lucky.

126
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:01,040
You don't need to say that he's lucky.

127
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,440
Miss Sai.

128
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,280
Mengmeng and the rest are gone.

129
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,600
Why are you still here?

130
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,480
I was afraid you would be lonely,

131
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,600
so I stayed to accompany you.

132
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,080
Enough with it.

133
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:14,200
You're clearly here
under orders from His Majesty

134
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,440
to manage the watercourse.

135
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,480
You want

136
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,520
to get the aqueduct blueprints
from me, don't you?

137
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,600
You say it so bluntly

138
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,560
that it becomes meaningless.

139
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:27,880
Who is it?

140
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,360
Who?

141
00:07:43,460 --> 00:07:45,100
[Noble Consort,
Yang City, Sai Residence]

142
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,120
Finally, Steward Lu and Guard Kong

143
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,520
have been stopped
from their third-wheeling.

144
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,320
Third-wheeling?

145
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:09,560
It's just how those in my hometown

146
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:11,600
speak of those who watch from the side.

147
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:14,880
Your hometown's language
is quite interesting.

148
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,560
That's why...

149
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:19,600
That's why when it comes
to you and your harem,

150
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:22,680
I am the third wheel.

151
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,280
Insolence!

152
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,880
My harem only has you.

153
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,080
Your Majesty.

154
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,960
Also, once I get back,

155
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,200
I'll have the Empress Dowager match us.

156
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,320
Match us?

157
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:34,400
What about Wan?

158
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,760
Wan only loves Qi Su.

159
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,120
I have my own plans.

160
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,160
Okay.

161
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,680
Why are those two not back yet

162
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,080
from their trip to buy food?

163
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:12,720
Let's get on the boat first.

164
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,080
Attack.

165
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:06,960
Mengmeng!

166
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,200
Mengmeng!

167
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:17,520
Let's go.

168
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,120
Hold on tight.

169
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,800
His Majesty will surely

170
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:36,040
love the food I bought.

171
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,040
After all, I've been with him
for so many years.

172
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:40,360
This...

173
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:46,360
Your Majesty!

174
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,400
Your Majesty!

175
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:48,800
What do we do?

176
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,080
Have you seen His Majesty?

177
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,200
His Majesty isn't here.

178
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,440
It must have been assassins.

179
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,320
Assassins?

180
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,200
Then...

181
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:56,880
Blood!

182
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,760
The assassins
must have been lying in wait

183
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,360
and attacked while we were gone.

184
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:05,320
It must be Chancellor Cui.

185
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,320
Right now, only he

186
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:08,040
doesn't want His Majesty
to return to the capital.

187
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,520
What do we do now?

188
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,200
We must find His Majesty soon.

189
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:18,680
Qi Yan,

190
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:19,920
is your wound okay?

191
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:21,720
Don't worry.

192
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:22,840
Mengmeng,

193
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,840
I will protect you.

194
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:34,200
Qi Yan.

195
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,000
Qi Yan.

196
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,240
I'm fine.

197
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,280
Let's go.

198
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:05,720
Qi Yan.

199
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:06,920
Qi Yan.

200
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:17,220
[Laifu Inn]

201
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:23,000
It really is an inn.

202
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,200
We're saved.

203
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:25,640
We're saved.

204
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:37,280
Qi Yan.

205
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,040
Qi Yan.

206
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,040
There is an inn here.

207
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,560
Hang on just a little longer.

208
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,640
Is anyone here?

209
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:51,920
Is anyone here?

210
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:53,200
Is anyone here?

211
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,280
You're up.

212
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:01,680
Where are we?

213
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,200
Stay here. Don't move.

214
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,840
I'll look for candles.

215
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,000
Qi Yan.

216
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:23,280
Qi Yan.

217
00:13:42,800 --> 00:13:43,520
I...

218
00:13:43,920 --> 00:13:46,280
I just want to clean your wound.

219
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,080
Does it hurt a lot?

220
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,120
It's fine.

221
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:14,800
I won't die from this.

222
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,080
Don't say that.

223
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:21,120
I won't let you cry too.

224
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:25,920
I haven't found clean water.

225
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:28,200
The medicine is what we had with us.

226
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,360
Just bear with it for today.

227
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:31,720
I'll start searching tomorrow.

228
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:41,960
You're bleeding.

229
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:43,840
I'm not.

230
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:45,320
It's your blood.

231
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:46,680
Really?

232
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,560
With you in my arms,

233
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,600
I don't hurt anymore.

234
00:15:18,760 --> 00:15:20,160
Are you going back to Ximi tomorrow?

235
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:21,280
What is it?

236
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,120
Can't bear to see me leave?

237
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:24,840
Why would I?

238
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:26,720
I'm just curious

239
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:27,920
about what Ximi is like.

240
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:29,640
I have never been to Ximi.

241
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:31,040
Ximi

242
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,560
has the bluest skies,

243
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:33,840
the strongest wines,

244
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,800
the most passionate citizens,

245
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,960
and the most unforgettable scenery.

246
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,480
Why don't you go back
with me as my guest?

247
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:43,160
Forget about being a guest.

248
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,520
However,

249
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:45,800
I can consider

250
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:47,640
expanding Sai Family Escort to Ximi.

251
00:15:47,640 --> 00:15:48,120
Okay.

252
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:49,280
I'll be waiting.

253
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:51,560
Make way!

254
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:53,040
Make way!

255
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,000
What's going on?

256
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,200
Pay attention!

257
00:15:56,680 --> 00:15:57,800
An arrest warrant
from the Imperial Court.

258
00:15:57,800 --> 00:15:59,000
Anyone who has seen these two

259
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,440
and assist us in arresting them

260
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,960
will be awarded 100 taels.

261
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:03,560
Anyone who has seen these two

262
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:04,800
and assist us in arresting them

263
00:16:04,800 --> 00:16:06,400
will be awarded 100 taels.

264
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:07,400
[Warrant]
Look carefully

265
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:08,120
at these two.

266
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:08,880
Isn't that...?

267
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:09,840
Those who assist us in arresting them

268
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:11,400
will be awarded 100 taels.

269
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:12,000
Something happened.

270
00:16:14,140 --> 00:16:16,340
[Warrant]

271
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:30,720
Qi Yan.

272
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:35,000
Qi Yan.

273
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,000
Wake up.

274
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:05,000
Help us!

275
00:17:05,280 --> 00:17:06,600
What is that noise?

276
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:08,000
I'm afraid it's another beggar.

277
00:17:08,120 --> 00:17:09,400
You must ignore them, Miss Cui.

278
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:11,640
Help us!

279
00:17:12,320 --> 00:17:13,240
He needs help.

280
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:15,080
Miss, let me do it.

281
00:17:15,080 --> 00:17:15,640
Miss.

282
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:17,560
Miss Cui.

283
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:19,560
- Help me!
- Miss Sai and Mister Li just left.

284
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:21,280
Before they left, they ordered us

285
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:22,880
not to leave unless we need to.

286
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:24,080
Sir!

287
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:26,160
